msgid ""
"Upload your demo, intro, graphic, music or wild. There's a category for "
"whatever you're creating."
msgstr ""
"Lataa demosi, introsi, grafiikkasi, musiikkisi tai wildisi. Luomallesi "
"löytyy kategoria."

